{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ffb004e6e9","title":"吴德给北京市职工的一封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"593f3a5983","index":0,"year":1966,"month":11,"day":10,"articleId":"ffb004e6e9","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"工商交通和财政","id":"1ffce755c0","type":"主题"},{"name":"吴德","id":"7f0393737e","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"300ec78d67","name":"吴德"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9dd684b6df","type":"title","text":"吴德给北京市职工的一封信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ffb004e6e9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"601bb3f9d5","type":"paragraph","text":"职工同志们：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ffb004e6e9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"decc10a53e","type":"paragraph","text":"我正开工作会议，不能来看你们，很抱歉。现在把你们关心的一些问题，提出个人意见和大家商量。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ffb004e6e9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0ba8578a46","type":"paragraph","text":"1、在这次文化大革命中，有些同志在政治上遭到打击，有的甚至被打成“反革命”，这是十分错误的。市委准备发一个通知，发到各单位，凡是革命群众，在文化大革命中受到迫害，被打成反革命的一律不算数，必须彻底平反，恢复名誉，并向这些同志赔礼道歉。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ffb004e6e9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3599a7cc44","type":"paragraph","text":"2、你们这次离开生产岗位，出来串联，发生在今日<人民日报>《再论抓革命、促生产》的社论之前，应当照发工资，同时也不能对你们有任何歧视。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ffb004e6e9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bd87a72af4","type":"paragraph","text":"3、你们应当很好地学习十六条，中央关于抓革命促生产的通知和今日<人民日报>的社论。这个社论是根据毛主席一贯指示的精神写的，今后你们应当按照社论的精神来办，要真正做得抓革命，促生产。学会在搞好文化大革命的同时，把生产搞得更好！更好！更好！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ffb004e6e9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6b643bae1c","type":"paragraph","text":"我恳切地希望你们回到工厂去，回到生产岗位上去，有什么具体情况和问题，随时写信告诉我，有关平反等问题可和市委工交政治部接洽，具体解决。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ffb004e6e9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6518fb783","type":"paragraph","text":"此致","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ffb004e6e9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a6852ee102","type":"paragraph","text":"敬礼","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ffb004e6e9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"43ac1fb1e8","type":"paragraph","text":"吴德","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ffb004e6e9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0764ecc7f7","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年十一月十日","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ffb004e6e9","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}